Package: pitchxg
Title: Pitch xG
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ozayr", "Mohammed", , "ozayr.mohammed@nhs.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A modular Shiny app visualising expected goals (xG) and
    expected threat (xT) for a full football team season using StatsBomb
    open data. Features interactive shot maps, player comparison tables,
    xG vs goals summaries, and explanatory captions for actionable
    insights.
